uiEntry.title: tx_statistics
uiEntry.tooltip: This shows information about your clan's campaign.

uiEntry.title: row_eventlog
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address)
function Select(sel) if sel then this:SetState("selected") else this:SetState("unselected") end end
function OnSelect() local p = UIComponent(this:Parent()) p:LuaCall("SelectItem", Address)
-- Notify event_log that an entry has been clicked local event_log = UIComponent( this:Parent("event_log") ) event_log:InterfaceFunction("NotifyEntryClicked") end

uiEntry.title: button_continue
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address)
function OnLClickUp() UIComponent(this:Parent()):InterfaceFunction("ContinueGame") end

uiEntry.title: string
uiEntry.tooltip: Your campaign need not end here - you have completed the victory conditions, but there are always more provinces to conquer and rival clans to defeat!

uiEntry.title: button_quit
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address)
function OnLClickUp() UIComponent(this:Parent()):InterfaceFunction("ExitGame") end

uiEntry.title: string
uiEntry.tooltip: This will quit this campaign and return you to the main menu.
